            . I am a <rs id="t18270913-123-viclabel702" type="occupation">cheesemonger</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-123-victim1283 t18270913-123-viclabel702"></join>, and live in Whitecross-street. On the 14th of July, between eleven and twelve o'clock at night, the prisoner came into my shop, and tasted some bacon and cheese, but bought none - another person came in, which took my attention;<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182709130086"></xptr>the prisoner went down the shop, round the counter, went up to my desk, on which was 5s. in copper - he went out. I went after him, and as I took hold of him, he dropped the paper of copper - I find he bears a most excellent character.</p>
